%h1 Downloadable data files

%p
  These data files are generated daily from the subset of our data that has been
  reviewed. If a file is unavailable, the text in question has not yet been reviewed.

%p
  All data files are released under the
  != link_to "CC BY-NC-SA 3.0", "http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/us/"
  license. Please make sure that you are familiar with the terms of this license before downloading any of the files below.

%h2 Data files

%table
  - Source.all.each do |s|
    %tr
      %td!= link_to s.author_and_title, s
      %td!= link_to_if export_file_available?("#{s.human_readable_id}.xml"), "PROIEL format", "/exports/#{s.human_readable_id}.xml"
      %td!= link_to_if export_file_available?("#{s.human_readable_id}.tiger"), "TigerXML format", "/exports/#{s.human_readable_id}.tiger"
      %td!= link_to_if export_file_available?("#{s.human_readable_id}.conll"), "CoNLL format", "/exports/#{s.human_readable_id}.conll"
      %td!= link_to_if export_file_available?("#{s.human_readable_id}.txt"), "Text format", "/exports/#{s.human_readable_id}.txt"

